While one is already boasted as an [[absolute defense]], the user — without the need of [[hand seals]] — instantly summons five [[Summoning: Rashōmon|Rashōmon]] gates to neutralise incoming attacks. The user can alter the positioning of all five gates, even if it is to change the trajectory of an attack. Not only were the combination of these gates able to redirect an attack as powerful as a [[Tailed Beast Ball]] [[Evil Disturbance Waltz|equipped]] with a [[Susanoo]] sword, but they remained standing upon impact.<ref>''Naruto'' chapter 621, page 8</ref>
